translate English day6_1b207cf6:


    br "\n I'm in a dream. I'm once again standing on muddy ground underneath a pure red sky. {w}I'm starting to feel at home in this otherwise loathsome place."


translate English day6_337441a5:


    extend "\n There's no one here giving me constant headaches. There's no silent stares as I enter the department office. There's no oppressive future, no miserable past."


translate English day6_ccc3531c:


    extend "\n When I'm here, there is only her and me."


translate English day6_46892ac6:


    extend "\n She's my abominable angel, a supremely pure being containing all the beauty in the world, illuminated by a divine glow."


translate English day6_0ea62940:


    extend "\n I feel extraordinarily lucky that someone as unworthy as myself was chosen to be graced by her holy presence. {w}I smile in gratitude, choking back the nausea that clogs my throat."


translate English day6_f091a040:



    nvl clear
    br "\n The corners of my forced smile quiver. My forehead is wrinkled in a way that cannot be reversed. {w}And no matter how much I try to endure it, I can't stop from moaning in disgust."


translate English day6_34964b05:


    extend "\n A soft hand touches my face, drenched in cold sweat. I close my eyes and feel a deceptively beautiful voice whisper into my ear."


translate English day6_eddaa4ff:


    extend "\n When was the last time I felt so at peace? {w}Definitely not during this lifetime. I feel like I finally have the freedom necessary to imagine my own future."


translate English day6_2dcdf9ab:


    extend "\n I'm nothing special, but I am talented in my own way."


translate English day6_fc589369:



    nvl clear
    br "\n I've done what I could. {w}Looking at what remains before me, I'm not sure there's anything left that I can accomplish."


translate English day6_9572813c:


    extend "\n Despite being far more ambitious than those around me, without a sense of responsibility, that passion only burned me, ultimately consuming myself and everything around me in flames."


translate English day6_0f57a78e:


    extend "\n I'm currently somewhere above or below that mountain of ash. {w}There is no trace of the original form it once took."


translate English day6_4e5de730:


    extend "\n Perhaps everything was an illusion from the start and I was never capable of anything at all."


translate English day6_02c5d412:


    extend "\n The ashen landscape forces me to look back at the past I abandoned, on my futile obsession forcing me to act like I never had a chance at rebirth."


translate English day6_c3271b59:



    nvl clear
    br "\n The refusal to do anything but cling to and grow overly dependent on nostalgically beautiful memories makes it impossible to solve the problems that arise in the present. {w}It's as if I've forgotten how to live along the way."


translate English day6_134a68ae:


    extend "\n I'd rather be crushed by sentiment and suffer momentary torment than be forced to forever feel the way I do right now."


translate English day6_5d981879:


    extend "\n When I open my eyes once more, I'm still in this revolting, bright red place. {w}The angel has her arms wrapped around me, and I am enveloped in her warmth."


translate English day6_b40cbe68:


    extend "\n My brain fog is so thick that my jaw hangs slack, despite my efforts at keeping my mouth shut. {w}Saliva pours from between my lips along with something solid, and in my frustration, I fall forward onto my face."


translate English day6_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day6_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day6_6142197f:


    br "\n But what lies in front of me isn't filth. {w}What I see are bright red intestines wrapped in a thin blue membrane, making them appear almost purple. There's beautiful veins tracing the surface and copious amounts of blood flowing through it all."


translate English day6_7d4b370e:


    extend "\n I should be used to seeing something like this by now, but it's somehow different. {w}It reminds me of an angel that's been snatched away from me, falling toward the sullied ground."


translate English day6_464aafd0:


    extend "\n The wound from the recent passage of a blade reveals a pure white rib poking out from within the chest cavity, which has been split in half."


translate English day6_f74d427e:


    extend "\n Packed inside this torso, I can see only two lungs and one heart which is still busy beating despite everything else about her having long since come to a halt."


translate English day6_c0f2fcf1:



    nvl clear
    br "\n I feel frozen in place, unable to look away from the blasphemously grotesque scene before me, the image being burned into my memory."


translate English day6_0e19c3c5:


    extend "\n Her squishy entrails burst forth from her stomach, falling amongst the corpses on the ground. {w}It's as if they were all one being from the very beginning."


translate English day6_93111814:


    extend "\n The pale corpse of a young lady, her body long since grown cold, lays there with an expression of agony on her face, her tongue protruding from her mouth which hangs open in a silent scream. {w}Her wings and hair lay spread around her body, the light already fading from her visage."


translate English day6_13b42cb0:


    extend "\n With her wings spread wide, exposing the literal pit of her stomach, she looks no different from a goose or chicken laid out in a butcher's shop."


translate English day6_03683b8c:



    nvl clear
    br "\n As my thoughts reach that conclusion, I close my eyes shut, which have been wide open until this point. {w}Pathetic sobs pour from my lips, and I can feel the vomit I've been struggling to hold back begin to bubble up to the surface."


translate English day6_070fd53b:


    extend "\n My spirit still manages to trace, albeit faintly, my past memories and dreams. {w}Without that feeble effort, even she would be lost to me..."


translate English day6_1ff55181:


    extend "\n The strength flows from my legs, and I collapse on top of her. Forcing my eyes to remain shut, I struggle to remain crouched over on my knees to keep our flesh from touching."


translate English day6_ea297814:


    extend "\n I smell the faintly sweet scent of fresh, raw meat. {w} Somehow, I just barely manage to press both my hands together."


translate English day6_34623401:


    extend "\n There is no one around to hear my prayers. Yet my cowardly spirit wants something to cling to."


translate English day6_1140667f:



    nvl clear
    br "\n As I put more force into my clasped hands, a completely unfamiliar sensation instantly cools my head. {w}It clears away the fog that's been shrouding my thoughts, bringing the world around me into sharp relief."


translate English day6_ab8cff0c:


    extend "\n It brings my sleep-addled mind back to reality. Though I've never felt anything like this before, I'm very certain I know what it is."


translate English day6_7d6d69cc:


    extend "\n It feels heavy in my hands, and yet lighter than I was expecting, with little resistance. A shock that resonates through my fingertips. A single action could bring everything to a halt."


translate English day6_056de86e:


    extend "\n The way a blade feels stabbing into a person's heart."


translate English day6_fc0bc1b6:



    nvl clear
    br "\n My eyes once again open wide, this time with fright. {w}A fountain of blood gushes out, instantly soaking my body and obscuring my vision."


translate English day6_97aa6e6c:


    extend "\n My hands are still clasped tightly together, as if seeking salvation. {w}But even from within that all too familiar sensation, there is a hint of something completely alien."


translate English day6_11f86ad6:


    extend "\n I hold a bright red knife in my hands."


translate English day6_5cf1f7d8:



    nvl clear
    "\n My eyes snap open just as I scream. {w}In a heightened state of hyper awareness, I feel as if all the blood has been drained from my body."


translate English day6_352dbd77:


    "My breathing is so frantic and out of control that I can't even wipe the cold sweat from my face. {w}The sound of my heart pounding frantically in my chest, as if about to burst right out, only adds to my overall discomfort."


translate English day6_c5dde036:


    "Wiping the sweat from the back of my cold neck does nothing to alleviate the goosebumps covering my entire body."


translate English day6_8540ad89:


    "I'm suddenly overcome by dread. I peek under the futon covers."


translate English day6_5b2e2559:


    "With trembling hands devoid of strength, I slowly pull up the hem of my pants so I can look inside. {w}What I see leaves me breathless with shock."


translate English day6_2a402284:


    et "White foam is oozing out, similar to what an insect's guts might look like after having its body crushed by a tremendous force."


translate English day6_76b2fe88_3:


    nvl clear


translate English day6_4f211ce7:


    "\n There's a pale shadow in a light gray corridor. {w}I lift my tired gaze, still not yet over the shock I experienced this morning."


translate English day6_df8faf4d:


    "Everyone told me yesterday that I could take the day off today, but I look like the spitting image of health itself, making their worries unfounded."


translate English day6_1b89c079:


    "I can move my arm easily without much effort. {w}All my wounds have healed completely, with hardly any lingering pain or stiffness, which is the scariest part of all."


translate English day6_61123a58:


    "Why am I okay? I'm sure that's what anyone would think after seeing the condition I'm in."


translate English day6_6e21e2e5:


    et "That's why they want to keep me locked up in this room. {w}There's no way I can sit here quietly while those kinds of thoughts fill my mind."


translate English day6_b0827907:


    nar "When I appear at the department office, everyone freezes for a moment, as if bracing themselves for something, but that's about it."


translate English day6_df737886:


    nar "I take a seat, ignoring their reaction. As I sit down in my usual spot, the bishop greets me in her usual lackadaisical way."


translate English day6_5c816a41:


    nar "This normalcy has a calming effect. {w}I forced myself here in the hopes of finding just that, though I still find it hard to relax."


translate English day6_0debcf3b:


    my "You made it, [na2]."


translate English day6_36066b7e:


    pl "Morning, Maya. {w}I'd feel bad taking the day off when you're here as usual, so hopefully you won't mind letting me help out."


translate English day6_8407b9e4:


    my "Huh? Are you sure? {w}I didn't suffer an injury like you did, [na2]..."


translate English day6_3f01a147:


    pl "It's no big deal. See? I'm back to normal!"


translate English day6_479867ea:


    nar "Naturally, Maya is no different from usual. {w}Or rather, she always looks so awkward that it'd be pretty hard to notice any changes from the norm."


translate English day6_988d770a:


    nar "Which is exactly why I have to keep a closer eye on her than usual. {w}It's still not enough to calm me down."


translate English day6_7539bcd7:


    my "I'm glad, though. {w}Thank you for coming in to help me out."


translate English day6_2649c4d1:


    nar "Her white back, shining out against the darkness. {w}That image alone remains in vivid detail within my foggy memory."


translate English day6_b0bade53:


    nar "The dimpled flesh scattered around her round face."


translate English day6_933b3e7a:


    nar "I realize my eyes are unconsciously tracing the contours of her clothes, the material seemingly thinner than usual, and I quickly look away."


translate English day6_99af0cc0:


    nar "She trusts me completely, and here I am, doing just *what* exactly?"


translate English day6_1e56e1c5:


    nar "And it's not just Maya. {w}I never cared before, but now I can't stop worrying about the people around me. And at the same time, I catch myself thinking about the most inane things."


translate English day6_a50059c3:


    my "What's wrong, [na2]? Still not feeling well?"


translate English day6_629ba174:


    pl "No, I just... I just didn't get enough sleep."


translate English day6_d5dfe1c3:


    my "Yeah? You've been saying that a lot lately, [na2]... Still not used to your pillow?"


translate English day6_7f61d064:


    pl "Speaking of which, I... {w}Actually, that's probably it. Sorry for making you worry about me."


translate English day6_8a50d3b1:


    my "It's fine. {w}You don't have to apologize. I'm the one who's always causing problems anyway..."


translate English day6_9ed1b2d4:


    nar "Our back and forth follows the same usual nonsensical routine. {w}We're pointedly refusing to bring up the events from last night."


translate English day6_dae6e055:


    nar "It's not like anything that weird or embarrassing happened, so why avoid it?"


translate English day6_8078bc06:


    nar "Everyone goes through a similar experience, right? {w}It's almost like a rite of passage into adulthood. {w}But also if that's the case, why doesn't anyone talk about it?"


translate English day6_bc6cc656:


    nar "As my brain is filled with a series of dirty thoughts, I feel my head throb with pain."


translate English day6_8ab5e5d3:


    nar "Hurry up and think about something else. Maybe getting some work done will distract me. {w}With that in mind, I go to open my locker and what I see inside clears my distracted thoughts instantly."


translate English day6_342ee8ed:


    nar "There's a tool inside that doesn't belong to me. {w}I close the door and check the number. There's no mistake that this is my locker."


translate English day6_77076cc8:


    ex1 "Oh! Sorry 'bout that! It's been empty for so long that I figured no one was using it." with sshake


translate English day6_d043e475:


    nar "The guy who pipes up expectantly, almost as if he'd been waiting for this moment, is the same guy I met the other day. {w}One of the guys who'd been with blondie."


translate English day6_b9747c56:


    nar "That was only a few days ago, though I wonder if he even remembers."


translate English day6_1935cd3b:


    nar "I can't help but feel repulsed by his full-faced grin, exposing a set of teeth riddled with cavities."


translate English day6_ffef04c5:


    nar "There's another priest standing nearby who appears even more grossed out than me. Upon seeing what's going on, he hurries over while shouting angrily."


translate English day6_3d094f65:


    ex2 "Hey! What did I tell you about cleaning up after yourself? You're gonna leave that mess for someone else to take care of?!" with sshake


translate English day6_49d5a6a5:


    nar "Ignoring me completely, the two engage in a light-hearted scuffle, intermixed with vulgar laughter."


translate English day6_39dfa5d9:


    nar "Trying to understand the situation playing out before me only leads to something simplistically childish."


translate English day6_beebd372:


    nar "But I'm able to pick up enough on things to feel hurt."


translate English day6_e71a9e59:


    nar "In the midst of the commotion, a woman who was busy grabbing her own tools right next to me speaks up."


translate English day6_d3e0048a:


    ex3 "I'm really sorry about that, but..."


translate English day6_3188eb15:


    ex3 "Well, we're pretty short on space around here. {w}If you're getting transferred over to the Magic Department soon anyway, it'd be great if you could clear out your locker."


translate English day6_14dfbbef:


    nar "I recognized her from having adjacent seats, though we'd never exchanged a single word before this moment."


translate English day6_572e4e4b:


    nar "Despite all that, she's acting unquestionably hostile toward me."


translate English day6_1f37ac74:


    nar "Her cool gaze never once meets mine throughout our entire conversation and the sound of her locker door slamming shut echoes out louder than necessary."


translate English day6_79dc8df5:


    nar "Glancing around, I realize she's not the only one."


translate English day6_fe4a6f3f:


    nar "I realize everyone is either sneering at me, glaring at me, or are acting outwardly hostile. They're treating me like I'm some strange curiosity."


translate English day6_4b79339d:


    nar "I'd felt slightly alienated from the rest of the group since day one, but that feeling of distance between us is practically flooding my senses."


translate English day6_208d8c6e:


    nar "There's nothing special about the guys who bullied me. {w}They're simply expressing their emotions in the only way they know how."


translate English day6_e0878c13:


    nar "The truth is that everyone here feels the same way about me. It's just most don't voice those opinions out loud."


translate English day6_badcae14:


    nar "I glare silently at the group of guys pulling tools from inside my locker, as if they were filth,"


translate English day6_0cda21c3:


    nar "waiting for their voices to finally vanish into the distance."


translate English day6_994d233e:


    nar "I can feel my blood slowly boiling inside my head, though inwardly, I feel more frustrated at myself for letting them get to me as much as they have."


translate English day6_e8958d9c:


    my "Hey, [na2]... Don't take it to heart, okay? {w}They're just jealous of you..."


translate English day6_a9288eab:


    nar "As the commotion dies down, I hear Maya speak up timidly from behind me. {w}I simply stand there, unable to look at her."


translate English day6_7031adc5:


    nar "I can see that awkward expression on her face clearly in my mind."


translate English day6_6daaf519:


    nar "How many times will I put this poor girl through this kind of situation? {w}I'm a mixed up mess of frustration and shame."


translate English day6_16cc31c6:


    pl "It's not that I necessarily want to move to the Magic Department, but..."


translate English day6_d6a4cc7b:


    nar "A rant I've been inadvertently holding back suddenly bubbles forth."


translate English day6_1476a0f0:


    nar "Ever since discovering what exactly the temple was like, I hadn't really wanted to move to the Magic Department."


translate English day6_7190ec66:


    nar "But look at the mess around me. {w}On one hand, there's the Cleanup Department's open hostility toward me. {w}Then there's the Magic Department's unrealistic expectations of me."


translate English day6_9b95f58c:


    nar "I feel as if I'm constantly being blamed for my choices while standing at the edge of a cliff. {w}This constant feeling of suffocation from being forced to do things is pissing me off."


translate English day6_1e33908e:


    nar "I don't really care if these losers are jealous of me for the blessing I received."


translate English day6_8f3de28d:


    nar "I shouldn't care. {w}If I was truly living the life of luxury they believe that I do, I wouldn't be suffering as much as I am."


translate English day6_0432ea6c:


    my "Don't say that..."


translate English day6_eb1e660c:


    pl "..."


translate English day6_d9e0804b:


    hk "Where is everyone?"


translate English day6_340fba8a:


    nar "Haku's unique drawl suddenly breaks up the tension in the room. {w}Both Maya and myself look up, startled."


translate English day6_64bb7e7c:


    nar "Through a gap in the door leading into the classroom, usually kept shut,"


translate English day6_535e8e68:


    nar "we're able to catch a glimpse of Haku, rolling her eyes in complete ignorance of the events that just transpired."


translate English day6_11335767:


    hk "What are you two still doing here?"


translate English day6_d4c33e83:


    my "W-We were just talking... {w}I'm on my way out..."


translate English day6_d67105bc:


    hk "Getting along and making friends is truly splendid... within reason, of course."


translate English day6_0354b326:


    hk "Ah... Brother [na]? Can I have a word?"


translate English day6_ef94174f:


    nar "She waves her sleeve in my direction before gesturing towards the door."


translate English day6_9d0e2dbc:


    nar "I point at myself to confirm she's addressing me before nodding compliantly."


translate English day6_d6202922:


    nar "I glance at Maya with a look of doomed resignation. {w}She responds with her own look of pity, as if sympathizing with my assumed plight."


translate English day6_e10bb72d:


    pl "I'm sorry, Maya. {w}I'll catch up as soon as we're done here."


translate English day6_b68a34e1:


    my "Sure... No rush."


translate English day6_f1828df4:


    nar "I wonder what she wants to talk to me about?"


translate English day6_6a186814:


    nar "The first time she'd called me into her office, I'd been surprised by how almost clerical everything looked with the desks and bookshelves neatly organized, {w}directly contrasting Haku's more laid-back personality."


translate English day6_3f5e788e:


    nar "The room was fairly warm due to the window being shut and a part of me wonders how she even got in here as a smokey scent tickles my nostrils."


translate English day6_4f38e0ec:


    nar "She gestures toward a chair and I sit down, glancing around the room."


translate English day6_982d2d06:


    nar "As I think back to the troubling incidents I've dealt with over the past few days, an irritating tension forms in my feet, crawling up my legs."


translate English day6_a199b1c5:


    hk "I'm surprised."


translate English day6_7bc0f7eb:


    nar "Those are the words she opens with. {w}I suddenly realize every single incident occurred in the same place. {w}I wait with bated breath for her to continue."


translate English day6_a1f6c837:


    nar "As she deliberately forces me to look her in the eyes, I notice her expression and movements seem less erratic than usual."


translate English day6_13e0958a:


    hk "The callous guidance I've provided has led to disaster befalling my fellow brethren."


translate English day6_c707f0db:


    pl "Are you talking about my injury from yesterday?"


translate English day6_4c243a15:


    nar "She remains silent for a moment, as if considering her response, or for potentially another reason. She slowly blinks both eyes before speaking."


translate English day6_300723df:


    hk "Yes."


translate English day6_28bf8a03:


    pl "Why the long pause?"


translate English day6_360caf8f:


    hk "I had a thought earlier."


translate English day6_7f7e2522:


    pl "About what?"


translate English day6_0a27673e:


    hk "I like to keep an eye on all my young students, carefully considering how to approach each and everyone."


translate English day6_cdc1111e:


    hk "But yet, now that the time has come, I can't seem to get my thoughts in the order that I wanted them in..."


translate English day6_7817f96c:


    pl "Sounds like you're nervous."


translate English day6_da775dbb:


    hk "Mm, more like overjoyed. {w}That I am finally able to express how I feel..."


translate English day6_c500a578:


    nar "It doesn't sound like she's having any trouble at all."


translate English day6_516f47f7:


    hk "How are you feeling?"


translate English day6_2171afb1:


    pl "Fine. {w}I don't have any pain and everything seems okay."


translate English day6_cde4abf4:


    hk "That's good to hear."


translate English day6_cdb39408:


    hk "The reason why I was so slow to respond earlier is... {w}out of simple concern that you are having trouble fitting in with the brethren in our department."


translate English day6_eb1e660c_1:


    pl "..."


translate English day6_bc45bd8e:


    pl "There's no need to worry about that. I'm entirely to blame for not fitting in here."


translate English day6_a0db80a6:


    pl "It has nothing to do with any callousness on your part. {w}Besides, it's only been about a week anyway."


translate English day6_4b69f3d3:


    hk "Is that so?"


translate English day6_a4d58796:


    nar "So that's what she wanted to talk about. {w}As my mood sinks, I feel the strength leave my body. It's far too late for either of us to do anything about what's going on."


translate English day6_74402b42:


    nar "After mumbling several meaningless excuses, an expression of sadness on her face, she hands me a piece of paper. {w}It's a transfer form."


translate English day6_f1c9ee9a:


    hk "Despite your accident, your transfer will proceed as planned."


translate English day6_eb1e660c_2:


    pl "..."


translate English day6_2acffaf2:


    hk "Brother?"


translate English day6_19139fc5:


    pl "I have until today to turn this in, right?"


translate English day6_bb92b5bd:


    hk "Correct. Do... you need until tomorrow to think it over?"


translate English day6_853154f4:


    pl "Yes. If possible."


translate English day6_edd6c601:


    hk "No problem. Tomorrow then."


translate English day6_4bac5db6:


    nar "I take the piece of paper from her while wondering about the oddity of my own actions. {w}If it doesn't truly bother me, then why am I second guessing myself?"


translate English day6_f462ba65:


    hk "Why did you come here when we told you to take the day off to rest, Brother?"


translate English day6_4047f4f3:


    pl "Huh?"


translate English day6_6d3eed5e:


    nar "The reason why I came here today... {w}I try to formulate a quick answer, but find that it's impossible."


translate English day6_34efdbb1:


    pl "Like I already mentioned, I feel fine, and it's not like I have much time left here... {w}Also, I worry about Maya.."


translate English day6_6c5dc0ad:


    hk "You're a truly kind soul, Brother [na]..."


translate English day6_49d22df0:


    hk "It truly makes me feel all warm and soft inside to see everyone getting along and treating each other with kindness!"


translate English day6_3b0d7d8e:


    nar "I can't help but chuckle inwardly on hearing her call me kind. {w}The laughter was more at myself than at her."


translate English day6_3a1e4207:


    nar "I've lived my whole life up until now without having once been described like that."


translate English day6_bc7ed136:


    nar "When most folks use the word \"kind,\" they usually mean that someone is transparently naive."


translate English day6_71f25cdf:


    nar "Not only is my entire personality a shell of what it once was, I realize how sensitive I've become. {w}In my opinion, Maya is the only example of an actually kind person here."


translate English day6_de2f16ab:


    nar "I lean back in my chair before lowering my voice."


translate English day6_1a885036:


    pl "How exactly did you become the Pestis, Your Excellency?"


translate English day6_a0868a5e:


    hk "Well..."


translate English day6_c0028994:


    hk "It happened that the Heavens questioned me about the sins I had committed as a child."


translate English day6_8aaae01d:


    hk "Though I honestly have no memory of this... {w}Which is why I engage in the act of repentance everyday."


translate English day6_027e87cf:


    pl "I'm surprised. {w}I never expected you to be so forthcoming about yourself."


translate English day6_b19973ae:


    nar "I'd been planning on taking advantage of an unintentional opening, but it's clear she has no intention of keeping her true form a secret."


translate English day6_4acfb5ff:


    nar "In that moment, any doubt or concern I might have held about her flies out the window."


translate English day6_4b62966c:


    hk "One should not try to hide their sins."


translate English day6_80e06cf9:


    hk "It's a personal pastime of mine, actually, confessing to each and every sin I have committed."


translate English day6_76b3e831:


    pl "I'm not sure I understand the point, to be honest."


translate English day6_bac5976e:


    hk "Secrets make sharpened thorns out of people, you know."


translate English day6_f7133df2:


    hk "Integrity breeds beauty, and I am rather proud of my attributes..."


translate English day6_12625944:


    pl "...I don't think I'll ever understand you, Your Excellency."


translate English day6_5cc6602c:


    hk "The point of a confession is not to be understood..."


translate English day6_c4e76184:


    hk "It is to be forgiven."


translate English day6_8ab71d59:


    pl "How can I forgive you if I don't understand?"


translate English day6_4ee47d84:


    hk "It is pure arrogance for one to expect another to understand their actions while accepting the existence of their sins."


translate English day6_6dd8e3e9:


